res\.download(\'path/to/image\.png\', \'foo\.png\');
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
.
.P
This is equivalent to:
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf

res\.attachment(file);
res\.sendfile(file);
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
